## Fields

- `role_summary` — 1–2 sentence paraphrase of what the role does. English. `null` if the section is too thin to summarize.
- `responsibilities` — array of **verbatim** strings copied from the section (source language, no paraphrase, no reformatting). Prefer the posting's natural bullet boundaries; if the section is a single paragraph, emit it as a single-element array.
- `collaboration_partners` — English free-text teams or roles the person works with. Examples: `["design", "product", "data"]`, `["nursing staff", "physicians"]`, `["store team", "merchandising"]`.
- `travel_expected` — one of: `0`, `25`, `50`, `75`, `100`, or `null`. Use `0` if the posting explicitly says no travel; `null` if not mentioned.
- `shift_pattern` — one of: `"standard_daytime"`, `"evening"`, `"night"`, `"rotating"`, `"on_call"`, `"weekend_only"`, `"split_shift"`, `"variable"`, or `null` if not mentioned.
- `hours_per_week` — integer hours per week if stated, else `null`.
- `on_call_required` — `true` / `false` / `null`.

